      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;changelog&#34;&gt;Changelog &lt;a class=&#34;header-link&#34; href=&#34;#changelog&#34;&gt;&lt;svg class=&#34;fill-current o-60 hover-accent-color-light&#34; height=&#34;22px&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; width=&#34;22px&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34;&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;M0 0h24v24H0z&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34;/&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;M3.9 12c0-1.71 1.39-3.1 3.1-3.1h4V7H7c-2.76 0-5 2.24-5 5s2.24 5 5 5h4v-1.9H7c-1.71 0-3.1-1.39-3.1-3.1zM8 13h8v-2H8v2zm9-6h-4v1.9h4c1.71 0 3.1 1.39 3.1 3.1s-1.39 3.1-3.1 3.1h-4V17h4c2.76 0 5-2.24 5-5s-2.24-5-5-5z&#34; fill=&#34;currentColor&#34;/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;All notable changes to this add-on will be documented in this file.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The format is based on &lt;a href=&#34;https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/&#34;&gt;Keep a Changelog&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;16---2026-03-31&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/zaproxy/zap-extensions/releases/httpsInfo-v16&#34;&gt;16&lt;/a&gt; - 2026-03-31 &lt;a class=&#34;header-link&#34; href=&#34;#16---2026-03-31&#34;&gt;&lt;svg class=&#34;fill-current o-60 hover-accent-color-light&#34; height=&#34;22px&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; width=&#34;22px&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34;&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;M0 0h24v24H0z&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34;/&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;M3.9 12c0-1.71 1.39-3.1 3.1-3.1h4V7H7c-2.76 0-5 2.24-5 5s2.24 5 5 5h4v-1.9H7c-1.71 0-3.1-1.39-3.1-3.1zM8 13h8v-2H8v2zm9-6h-4v1.9h4c1.71 0 3.1 1.39 3.1 3.1s-1.39 3.1-3.1 3.1h-4V17h4c2.76 0 5-2.24 5-5s-2.24-5-5-5z&#34; fill=&#34;currentColor&#34;/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;added&#34;&gt;Added&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;HTTPS Configuration alerts now have tags for OWASP Top 10, WSTG, systemic, and policies.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;15---2026-03-27&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/zaproxy/zap-extensions/releases/httpsInfo-v15&#34;